表的代码预览贷款

drop index loans_PK on loans;


alter table loans
drop foreign key FK_LOANS_发放贷款_BRANCH;

drop table if exists loans;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: loans */
/*==============================================================*/
create table loans
(
loan_id varchar(60) not null comment '',
branch_name varchar(255) comment '',
amount float(8,2) comment '',
times int comment ''
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: loans_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index loans_PK on loans
(
loan_id
);

alter table loans add constraint FK_LOANS_发放贷款_BRANCH foreign key (branch_name)
references branch (branch_name) on delete restrict on update restrict;
